'''梅格斯综合症'''（{{lang-en|Meigs syndrome, Meigs' syndrome}}），是一类三重综合症，包括[[腹水|腹水]]、[[胸腔积液|胸腔积液]]和原发性[[卵巢肿瘤|卵巢肿瘤]]（比如[[纤维瘤|纤维瘤]]、[[布伦内罗氏瘤|布伦内罗氏瘤]]或偶然的[[卵巢颗粒细胞瘤|卵巢颗粒细胞瘤]]）<ref name="ReferenceA">{{EMedicine|article|255450|Meigs syndrome}}</ref><ref name="pmid16515612">{{cite journal |author=Morán-Mendoza A, Alvarado-Luna G, Calderillo-Ruiz G, Serrano-Olvera A, López-Graniel CM, Gallardo-Rincón D |title=Elevated CA125 level associated with Meigs' syndrome: case report and review of the literature |journal=Int. J. Gynecol. Cancer |volume=16 |issue=Suppl 1 |pages=315–318 |year=2006 |pmid=16515612 |doi=10.1111/j.1525-1438.2006.00228.x}}</ref><ref name=shaw>{{cite book|last=Padubidri, Daftary|title=Shaw's Textbook Of Gynaecology, 15e|year=2011|url=https://archive.org/details/howkinsbournesha0000unse|publisher=Elsevier India|isbn=9788131225486|page=[https://archive.org/details/howkinsbournesha0000unse/page/385 385]}}</ref>。

手术方式通常是对肿瘤部位的{{link-en|节段性切除术|Segmental resection}}。因为经横膈的淋巴管通常在右侧变大，而胸腔积液经常发生于右侧。对胸腹腔积液的病理学研究仍然不明<ref name="ReferenceA"/>。梅格斯综合症是以{{link-en|乔·文森特·梅格斯|Joe Vincent Meigs}}命名<ref>{{WhoNamedIt|synd|2351|Meigs' syndrome}}</ref><ref name="pmid10996681">{{cite journal |author=Lurie S |title=Meigs' syndrome: the history of the eponym |journal=Eur. J. Obstet. Gynecol. Reprod. Biol. |volume=92 |issue=2 |pages=199–204 |year=2000 |pmid=10996681 |doi=10.1016/S0301-2115(99)00289-4 |url=http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0301211599002894 |access-date=2013-10-30 |archive-date=2018-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180605003718/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0301211599002894 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="pmid13148256">{{cite journal |author=Meigs JV |title=Fibroma of the ovary with ascites and hydrothorax; Meigs' syndrome |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_american-journal-of-obstetrics-and-gynecology_1954-05_67_5/page/962 |journal=Am. J. Obstet. Gynecol. |volume=67 |issue=5 |pages=962–85 |pmid=13148256 |date=May 1954}}</ref>。

==诊断==
梅格斯综合征可能会被误诊为其他病情<ref name="pmid19161612">{{cite journal |author=Lanitis S, Sivakumar S, Behranwala K, Zacharakis E, Al Mufti R, Hadjiminas DJ |title=A case of Meigs syndrome mimicking metastatic breast carcinoma |journal=World J Surg Oncol |volume=7 |pages=10 |year=2009 |pmid=19161612 |pmc=2633000 |doi=10.1186/1477-7819-7-10 |url=http://www.wjso.com/content/7//10 |access-date=2013-10-30 |archive-date=2019-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191213012723/http://www.wjso.com/content/7//10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。因为腹水和胸腔积液的出现，错误的诊断包括有[[肝功能衰竭|肝功能衰竭]]（[[肝硬化|肝硬化]]）、[[充血性心力衰竭|充血性心力衰竭]]、[[肾脏疾病|肾脏疾病]]或进入腹膜表面的[[转移瘤|转移瘤]]。这些问题需要在临床中进行排除。

==治疗==
治疗梅格斯综合征的方法包括有{{link-en|胸腔穿刺术|thoracentesis}}和{{link-en|腹腔穿刺术|paracentesis}}，将多余的液体（渗出液）析出，并且采用单边的{{link-en|卵巢切除术|oophorectomy}}或楔形切除术去除疾患根源。

